query:
DELETE
            FROM domains d
                USING projects p
            WHERE (d.project_id IS NULL OR
                   (
                       d.project_id = p.id
                           AND d.project_id = $2
                           AND p.organization_id = $1
                       )
                )
              AND (d.organization_id IS NULL OR
                   (d.organization_id = $1
                        AND $2::uuid IS NULL)
                  )
              AND (d.id = $3)
            RETURNING d.id
